  <thing id="cDoOUmSpDe" name="Speak with Dead" description="At 2nd level, a Disciple of Orcus can {i}speak with dead{/i} as the spell once per day and an additional time per day for every 3 Disciple levels thereafter (2 at 5th, 3 at 8th). The ability functions as if cast by a caster of a level equal to the Disciple&apos;s total divine spellcaster character levels." compset="ClSpecial">
